### Emails not sending in production
**Cause**: Email API key for production not set, OR sending from unverified domain
```typescript
// ✅ FIX — verify domain in Resend/SendGrid dashboard
// "From" address MUST use a verified domain:
// ✅ from: 'hello@yourdomain.com'
// ❌ from: 'hello@gmail.com'  (blocked by email providers)

// Check RESEND_API_KEY is set in Netlify env vars
// Test in production by checking email provider dashboard logs
```

