### Preview broken / scripts blocked / CSP violation in next.config
**Cause**: Content Security Policy headers in `next.config.ts` are missing required domains for Supabase, analytics, and Rocket.new preview URLs. Browser console shows `Refused to load script` or `connect-src` errors.

**Root file**: `next.config.ts` (or `next.config.js`) — the `headers()` function

```typescript
// ✅ FIX — ensure these directives are in your CSP headers() block in next.config.ts

const securityHeaders = [
  {
    key: 'Content-Security-Policy',
    value: [
      "default-src 'self'",
      "script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' 'unsafe-eval' https://www.googletagmanager.com https://www.google-analytics.com https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com https://static.rocket.new",
      "script-src-elem 'self' 'unsafe-inline' 'unsafe-eval' https://www.googletagmanager.com https://www.google-analytics.com https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com https://static.rocket.new",
      "connect-src 'self' https://*.supabase.co wss://*.supabase.co https://api.openai.com https://bws.bioid.com https://*.bioid.com https://api.tryterra.co https://appanalytics.rocket.new",
      "img-src 'self' data: blob: https:",
      "font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com",
      "style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com",
      "frame-src 'self'",
    ].join('; '),
  },
]

// In next.config.ts:
const nextConfig = {
  async headers() {
    return [
      {
        source: '/(.*)',
        headers: securityHeaders,
      },
    ]
  },
}
```

**Quick diagnosis**: Open browser DevTools → Console tab → look for:
- `Refused to load script from '...'` → missing from `script-src`
- `has been blocked by CORS policy` → missing from `connect-src`
- `refused to connect` (WebSocket) → missing `wss://` in `connect-src`

**Most common missing entries by symptom**:
| Symptom | Add to CSP |
|---|---|
| Supabase realtime broken | `wss://*.supabase.co` in connect-src |
| Google Analytics not firing | `https://www.googletagmanager.com` in script-src |
| OpenAI calls blocked | `https://api.openai.com` in connect-src |
| Rocket preview banner missing | `https://static.rocket.new` in script-src |
